dct_creator_sm: Community Development Agency, County of Marin, California
dct_description_sm: A sphere of influence is a plan adopted by LAFCO for the probable physical boundaries and service areas of a city or special district.  Marin Resource Conservation District Sphere of Influence is a topologically correct polygon representation of sphere of influence boundaries of the Marin Resource Conservation District of Marin County.
dct_publisher_sm: San Rafael (Calif.). County Of Marin Community Development Agency.
dct_title_s: Marin Resource Conservation District Sphere of Influence
